{"word":"ὑπερεμέω","slug":"ὑπερεμέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n107458\" key=\"u(pereme/w\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ὑπερεμέω</orth>, <sense id=\"n107458.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">vomit violently</tr_>: metaph. of over-full veins, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">cause suffusion,</tr_> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ὑπερεμήσαντα τὰ φλέβια</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0627.tlg023:2:17\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hp.\">Hp.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Morb.\">Morb.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.17</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἢν ὑπερεμήσωσιν αἱ φλέβες</foreign> ib.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0627.tlg023:18\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">18</biblScope> </bibl> (<foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">-εμέσ-</foreign> ib.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0627.tlg023:4\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4</biblScope> </bibl>): hence <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ὑπερέμετος</orth>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ὁ</gen>, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">over-fullness of the veins,</tr_> ib.<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0627.tlg023:4\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4</biblScope> </bibl> (vv.ll. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὑπερεμέειν, ὑπεραίμετον</foreign>): but forms of <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὑπεραιμέω</foreign> (q. v.) shd. prob. be restored; the corruption has been helped by the words of <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hp.\">Hp.</a></author></bibl>, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τὸ μὲν οὔνομα οὐκ ὀρθὸν τῇ νούσῳ, οὐ γὰρ ἀνυστὸν ὑπεραιμῆσαι </foreign>(<foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">-εμῆσαι</foreign> codd.) <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">οὐδὲν τῶν φλεβίων κτλ.; ὑπεραιμήσειε</foreign> stands in <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0627.tlg023:2:4\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Morb.\">Morb.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.4</biblScope> </bibl> cod. G.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}